  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposal, by reason of its location, lack of natural light, and lack of direct and visible access from the public highway, and for which no marketing has been undertaken, represents an inappropriate use of the rear of the host building and would fail to provide suitable business space. The proposal would also fail to contribute to placemaking, to the detriment of future occupiers of the unit and the general amenity of the area. As such the proposal is contrary to policies D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) and D4 (Delivering good design) of the London Plan 2021 and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP26 (Employment Land and Floorspace) of the Hackney Local Plan 2020.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
